        "title": "Wireless TWS Stereo Earbuds",
        "description": "\n <p><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"4\" color=\"#46acc8\"><b><i><u>*Features*:</u></i></b></font></p>\n <ul>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\">Deliver crisp clear stereo sound </font></li>\n  <font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\">Easily pair with universal wireless-enabled device like smartphone,tablet,iPhone,iPad,laptop Built-in noise-reducing microphone One button answering/hanging up/rejecting hands-free calls and redialing the last number dialed </font>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\">Automatic voice prompt including incoming phone number report </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\">Each of the earbuds can be used alone with full functionality </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\">Share your favorite tunes with friend anytime anywhere by sharing the earbuds </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\">Lightweight,snug and comfortable design </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\">Includes a charging pod for convenient charging and storage </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\">CE and RoHS certified </font></li>\n </ul>\n <p><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"4\" color=\"#46acc8\"><b><i><u>*Specifications*:</u></i></b></font></p>\n <ul>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\">Earbuds: </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> Wireless Version: V4.2+EDR </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> Protocols Supported: HSP, HFP, A2DP, AVRCP </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> Transmission Range: ≤12M/39ft </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> Driver Unit: Ф7mm </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> Impedance: 32ohm±15% </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> Talk Time: (One Earbud): 5-6 hours; (Two Earbuds): 4-5 hours </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> Play Time: (One Earbud): 5-6 hours; (Two Earbuds): 4-5 hours </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> Standby: (One Earbud): 120 hours; (Two Earbuds): 70 hours </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> Charge Time: 1-2 hours </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> Battery: built-in 3.7V 75mAh li-ion battery per earbud </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> Size(per earbud): 0.94” x 0.71” x 1.1”/2.4 x 1.8 x 2.8cm (L x W x H) </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> Weight(per earbud): 5g/0.17oz </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> Available Color: black, white </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> Charging Pod: </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> Battery: built-in 3.7V 950mAh li-ion battery </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> Charging Voltage: DC 5V </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> Size of Charging Pod: 3.27” x 1.5” x 1.3”/8.3 x 3.8 x 3.3cm (L x W x H) </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> Weight of Charging Pod: 42g/1.48oz </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> Package size: 3.74” x 1.57” x 6.1”/9.5 x 4 x 15.5cm (L x W x H) </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> Package weight: 165g/0.36lbs</font></li>\n </ul>\n <p><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"4\" color=\"#46acc8\"><b><i><u>*Package Lists*:</u></i></b></font></p>\n <ul>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\">1 × Pair of Wireless Stereo TWS Earbuds </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> 2 × Pair of Replacement Eartips </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> 1 × USB Charging Cable </font></li>\n  <li><font size=\"3\" face=\"Times New Roman\"> 1 × User Manual</font></li>\n </ul>\n",
